has got me steamed...<br>
<br>
Being a bard.... <br>
<br>
Okay...breath...<br>
<br>
It seems that the latest patch Nerfed Bard speed... how you say?<br>
<br>
By nerfing bard percussion instruments.<br>
<br>
But wait there's more....<br>
<br>
They knew about this nerf before they finished doing the patch... and have bothered to make a correction for it ... Oh, but you have to wait till we patch again to see the reaction.... <br>
<br>
M'kay.. so that means ... We don't like Bards enough to fix stuff we break on them until it is convient?...<br>
<br>
WTF?<br>
<br>
NPC breaks... emergency patch<br>
Zones break... emergency patch<br>
Druid spell breaks... emergency patch<br>
Caster spell breaks, or nerfs... emergency patch<br>
Melee class damage something rather breaks... emergency patch<br>
<br>
Bards instruments break... well you have to wait.<br>
<br>
One of the most important advantages a bard has is there ability to move quickly... we don't get to port, we don't get to do uber amounts of damage... we do get to fly across a zone at lightning speed... but now... atleast until the Gods decide to fix it... we don't.<br>
